<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:30:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人质家属飞往海牙向哈马斯提出战争罪申诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</link><description>在接下来的几周内，已获释的人质预计将在闭门听证会上作证</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦领导人阿巴斯在结束战争和继续掌权之间走钢丝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总统向哈马斯公开请求的时机引起了巴勒斯坦街头的不满，许多人将其与他受到卡塔尔的压力联系起来</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 23:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</guid></item><item><title>在即时阴谋时代，一个简单的拼写错误就会引发病毒般的仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</link><description>唉，人为错误并不像另一个由于人们无法接受哈马斯令人发指的行为的现实而编造的不成比例的不切实际的寓言那么令人兴奋</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 21:47:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争后谁应该领导巴勒斯坦人？如何领导？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-should-lead-the-palestinians-after-the-gaza-war-and-how/0000018d-a81d-d0cb-a5ef-bb3f13cc0000</link><description>这些是巴勒斯坦人应该问的关键问题，即谁将领导他们 — — 以及尽管有西方政策制定者的支持，大人物和守旧派无法遵守的指导原则</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 20:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-should-lead-the-palestinians-after-the-gaza-war-and-how/0000018d-a81d-d0cb-a5ef-bb3f13cc0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属谴责内塔尼亚胡命令以色列代表团不要返回开罗进行进一步谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-slam-netanyahu-for-ordering-delegation-to-back-out-of-cairo-talks/0000018d-a8ae-d61b-a19d-efaf32dd0000</link><description>经过一天的会谈后，调解人建议双方继续与下级代表团进行讨论，但内塔尼亚胡以哈马斯拒绝屈服其要求为由拒绝了这一提议。人质家属打算在特拉维夫以色列国防军总部外露营以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 18:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-slam-netanyahu-for-ordering-delegation-to-back-out-of-cairo-talks/0000018d-a8ae-d61b-a19d-efaf32dd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 131 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-131/0000018d-a8c7-d0cb-a5ef-bbef8d580000</link><description>据报道，开罗人质释放/停火协议谈判延长了 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯呼吁哈马斯达成释放人质协议，以免巴勒斯坦人民遭受进一步的“灾难” ■ 白宫拒绝回答拜登是否相信内塔尼亚胡是诚实的中间人 ■ 一名以色列士兵被杀，以色列北部遭受来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击，造成 8 人受伤 ■ 战争开始 131 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 18:07:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-131/0000018d-a8c7-d0cb-a5ef-bbef8d580000</guid></item><item><title>自卫和人体盾牌：以色列应如何在加沙发动战争？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/self-defense-and-human-shields-how-should-israel-wage-war-in-gaza/0000018d-a6e9-dd3b-a5df-bfeb98e50000</link><description>当以色列威胁在庇护着超过一百万平民的加沙城市拉法进行重大行动时，它面临着艰难的道德和法律选择。当哈马斯试图最大限度地扩大对巴勒斯坦平民的伤害时，以色列国防军如何才能最大限度地减少对巴勒斯坦平民的伤害？</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 17:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/self-defense-and-human-shields-how-should-israel-wage-war-in-gaza/0000018d-a6e9-dd3b-a5df-bfeb98e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在以色列北部军事基地被真主党火箭弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/idf-soldier-killed-by-hezbollah-rocket-at-army-base-in-northern-israel/0000018d-a877-d0cb-a5ef-bb7fb2330000</link><description>一枚真主党火箭弹损坏了萨法德市北方司令部基地的两座建筑，20 岁的奥马尔·萨拉·本乔 (Omer Sarah Benjo) 被杀，八名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 17:12:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/idf-soldier-killed-by-hezbollah-rocket-at-army-base-in-northern-israel/0000018d-a877-d0cb-a5ef-bb7fb2330000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯和伊朗对特拉维夫发动袭击”：中国对以色列的虚假信息一瞥</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/russia-and-iran-launch-strike-on-tel-aviv-a-glimpse-into-chinese-disinfo-on-israel/0000018d-a7e3-da7e-a5ad-e7f32a000000</link><description>数十个虚假 YouTube 频道推出了数百个人工智能配音视频，内容涉及从加沙战争到微芯片等各种内容，所有这些都是为了帮助北京，甚至不惜牺牲以色列的利益</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 16:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/russia-and-iran-launch-strike-on-tel-aviv-a-glimpse-into-chinese-disinfo-on-israel/0000018d-a7e3-da7e-a5ad-e7f32a000000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯敦促哈马斯接受人质协议，以防止另一场“灾难”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-president-abbas-urges-hamas-to-accept-a-hostage-deal-to-prevent-catastrophe/0000018d-a810-d0cb-a5ef-bb3e85ad0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构主席呼吁尽快达成协议，以“防止巴勒斯坦人民遭受苦难”，并表示加沙战争的影响“比 1948 年大灾难更严重”</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:29:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-president-abbas-urges-hamas-to-accept-a-hostage-deal-to-prevent-catastrophe/0000018d-a810-d0cb-a5ef-bb3e85ad0000</guid></item><item><title>普京领导下的前高级官员资助特拉维夫大学新的俄罗斯研究中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/former-official-under-putin-helps-fund-new-russian-studies-center-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018d-a7eb-dc85-a9af-bfff55530000</link><description>自乌克兰战争爆发后离开俄罗斯以来，阿纳托利·丘拜斯一直居住在以色列。该大学表示所有学术活动都将由教师进行，排除了不当行为的可能性</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:29:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/former-official-under-putin-helps-fund-new-russian-studies-center-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018d-a7eb-dc85-a9af-bfff55530000</guid></item><item><title>米莱在以色列：阿根廷总统在动荡时期进行个人旅行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/milei-in-israel-argentine-president-goes-on-a-personal-journey-at-a-time-of-unrest/0000018d-a76c-d9a5-afdd-b76d1ed50000</link><description>在上周对以色列进行为期三天的访问期间，自由主义极右翼阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱与以色列政府的立场完全一致，这在圣地和国内引发了人们对他的动机的质疑</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:20:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/milei-in-israel-argentine-president-goes-on-a-personal-journey-at-a-time-of-unrest/0000018d-a76c-d9a5-afdd-b76d1ed50000</guid></item><item><title>名人签署公开信支持以色列参加欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</link><description>包括知名犹太名人在内的数百名娱乐业资深人士支持欧洲广播联盟将以色列纳入今年欧洲电视网比赛的承诺，尽管在加沙持续战争中要求将以色列排除在外的呼声很高</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</guid></item><item><title>五年后，耗资 3000 万谢克尔，东耶路撒冷缆车项目仍滞留在半空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</link><description>尽管该州一年多来一直在努力寻找一家国际公司来建设缆车网络，但西尔万的巴勒斯坦居民的土地仍然被征用，橄榄树也被连根拔起</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 14:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党的威慑平衡取决于哈马斯在开罗的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉再次表示，尽管以色列努力将黎巴嫩问题单独对待，但只有在加沙达成停火后，才会在北部边境达成协议。球在以色列这边，但以色列对真主党的要求不仅仅是停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</guid></item><item><title>SUV 盗窃浪潮引发人们对来自约旦河西岸的另一场 10 月 7 日式袭击的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</link><description>过去几周，以色列发生了铃木吉姆尼盗窃案。许多人再次出现在约旦河西岸，导致一些人担心这些盗窃行为是袭击计划的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹，导致一名以色列人死亡、八人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</link><description>炮火攻击的目标是以色列北部城市萨法德的一个军事基地；以色列国防军表示正在回应并打击黎巴嫩的火源</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属前往国际法庭敦促起诉哈马斯领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</link><description>以色列不是国际刑事法院成员，也不承认其管辖权，但检察官卡里姆·汗本周重申，该法院对 10 月 7 日事件拥有管辖权。人质家属代表团希望法院逮捕哈马斯领导人认股权证</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</guid></item><item><title>“严重关切”：犹太领导人致信以色列外长，谴责部长们与瑞典极右翼政党的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</link><description>在给以色列外交部长的一封信中，欧洲犹太人大会和瑞典犹太社区理事会的领导人警告不要与瑞典民主党结盟，信中称瑞典民主党“自称是我们的盟友”，同时主张“犹太人不能是瑞典人” .&amp;#39;该党根源于新纳粹和反犹太主义意识形态</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空表示，由于战时低成本航站楼关闭，该公司取消了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</link><description>瑞安航空在 10 月 7 日取消飞往以色列的航班后仅两周前就续签了部分航线。这家总部位于都柏林的航空公司在周二发布的一份声明中表示，“期待在低成本航站楼 1 号航站楼重新开放后恢复运营”。打开&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>